exhibitor: San Francisco Conservatory of Flowers, Eric Imperiale

measurements.description: One thousand nine hundred thirty-six flowers and 300 buds on 2236 inflorescences; grown in an elongated tree fern cylinder creating an 86-cm circumference ball ; flowers bell shaped, sepals, petals and lip orange basally, yellow distally; anther cap yellow; substance very firm; texture glossy; noted for being an extremely clean and well-groomed plant.
